Social Media Updates Every Business Owners Should Know
text:
Is your business already on social media? Are you using videos in your marketing campaigns? Then you'll be interested in these latest updates from TikTok, Instagram, and YouTube!

Instagram Story - videos under 60 seconds in stories will no longer be split into segments

TikTok - announced a huge increase in its video descriptions from 150 to 200 to now 2,200 characters

YouTube - outlines new monetization program for Shorts Creators

Short-form videos are exploding! And so the battle of the big players in the video industry begins.
